'''Jamie Hyneman''' worked for [[Industrial Light & Magic|ILM]] on the prequel movies [[Star Wars: Episode I The Phantom Menace|''The Phantom Menace'']] and [[Star Wars: Episode II Attack of the Clones|''Attack of the Clones'']].

He co-hosted the ''MythBusters'' show on the Discovery Channel, along with [[Adam Savage]]. In 2014, they hosted a ''[[MythBusters Star Wars Special]]'' episode.

Hyneman voiced a member of the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]] along with Savage on ''[[Phineas and Ferb: Star Wars]]''.<ref name="phineas">{{WebCite|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2014/07/18/phineas-and-ferb-star-wars-special-exclusive-image-reveal|text=IGN - Phineas & Ferb: Star Wars Special Exclusive Image Reveal|archivedate=20160603065901}}</ref>

